wiki.content: According to the Hurricane Songfacts, on this song Jared Leto asks the question "Where is your God?" Other tracks on This Is War also feature lyrics where he appears to be questioning faith. Kerrang! asked him about this. Leto replied: "Faith is an important topic on the record. There is a sense of a quest there. I haven't reached any resolution in that quest, but it's important to ask questions."
